{"tid":1579554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21號死城計劃 得閒的全部去大西北屯門","createTime":"2019-09-18T15:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T18:14:17.000Z","uid":94771,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"23c62192b0b45187c30b729bec375e4a9c924ae2","tid":1579554,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"大家都知21號何妖吹大雞 咁撚鐘意撕就又佢撕啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>我地22號再貼過新的 反正我地都要位做10.1 9.29/9.28新文宣</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貼得更大更闊更強更多<br />\n<br />\n反正人地吹大雞 但我地又唔想鐘個頭埋去 佩合佢地計劃 <br />\n雙方進行打鬥 做成人民打人民現像<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emxpnYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemxpnYU.jpg&h=c4627409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>個日日又有活動去屯門行街/踢波 點解要故意同佢地玩</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mH9jbR9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmH9jbR9.jpg&h=a1d83eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔去行街/踢波的 都希望你地唔好出街啦 <br />\n你知人地何律師好撚勁 好撚疊馬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地後面又有POPO幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚危險 建議大家個日就唔好出街啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有做生意的都唔好做啦 你知啦人地<strong>人強馬壯 </strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又大權利 保障自己 唔開好過開 錢可以搵返 命仔無佐就無了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85422a671faf5c44308be0cf54214677398fb56f","tid":1579554,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52138a1a82fd99503